              border-left: 3px solid #4c305f;
              padding-left: 14px;
              margin-bottom: 15px;
            "><strong>Moldova's referendum</strong> on joining the European Union narrowly passed. The result reflects growing pro-European sentiment in the country, although not as fast as some would like (<a href="https://www.dw.com/en/moldova-narrowly-votes-yes-to-eu-membership/a-70544401" target="_blank">read more</a>).</p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.4;
              border-left: 3px solid #4c305f;
              padding-left: 14px;
              margin-bottom: 15px;
