          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.4;
              border-left: 3px solid #4c305f;
              padding-left: 14px;
              margin-bottom: 15px;
            ">During his surprise visit to Kyiv, U.S. Defense Secretary Lloyd Austin announced a new <strong>$400 million military aid</strong> package for Ukraine (<a href="https://euromaidanpress.com/2024/10/21/pentagon-chief-announces-400-mn-aid-package-during-kyiv-visit/" target="_blank">read more</a>).</p>
        </mj-text>
